         Level gives a pet (or any average npc) several things.</P><P>-Hits for more each hit (better innate DAM)<BR>-Hits more often (more atk)<BR>-Gets hit less often (more avoidance AC)<BR>-Gets hit for less (more mitigation AC)<BR>-Has more HP</P><P>Pet level is a big deal.</P><P><BR>Noct<BR>17th Necromancer Chomedome of Ayonae Ro<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
